# Project: Chimera SDK

AI-powered user guidance platform. Drop-in SDK that observes web app user behavior, detects stuck/confused states, and delivers contextual help — or stays silent when users are in flow.

## Packages
- `@chimera/sdk` (npm) — JS/TS frontend: event collection, widget, spatial overlay
- `chimera-sdk` (PyPI) — Python backend: flow registration, rules, analytics API

## Commands
- `uv run python main.py` — run backend
- `uv install <package>` — add Python dependency
- `black <file>` — format Python (always run after changes)

## Parent project
Inherits patterns from CHIMERA (`/home/_3ntropy/dev/chimera`). See `docs/daemon-project-handoff.md`.

## Build order
1. JS event collector → 2. Backend event pipeline → 3. Rules classifier → 4. Hypervisor → 5. Widget → 6. Spatial overlay → 7. Memory → 8. Dashboard → 9. Multi-tenant → 10. NPM + PyPI
